Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:51.10,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:53.33,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:56.62,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:00.18,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,A candy store called Urahara’s Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:03.94,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.14,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.19,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:15.55,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:17.76,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you were \Nhaving a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:18.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.83,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:27.34,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,What…is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.90,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:31.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve never seen me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.97,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,It’s me, Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:38.09,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why were those guys after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.51,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of something you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.09,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, before we get to that…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:43.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a Soul Reaper, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:44.90,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You should’ve said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:48.43,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Not to brag, but I’m pretty \Nknowledgeable in that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.20,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:51.72,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right, lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:56.89,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not in this form by choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:58.69,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a Mod Soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so when I can’t use Ichigo’s body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s nothing I can do about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.52,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,A Mod Soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.79,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,T-That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.39,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What’re you staring at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:19.99,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, answer my questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:24.01,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,My loyal servants might \Nbe able to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.52,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Perverted freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:33.99,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.17,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.41,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:43.07,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was ask her questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.16,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn’t want to talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s no use trying \Nto force it out of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.48,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.29,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.07,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother and the others waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.25,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I’ll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.07,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,All right then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.87,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Off we go to the strategy meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:08.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You stay by her with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.02,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.10,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,She is being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.55,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,We need to take precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.67,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:16.98,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s an important assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:18.25,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:25.04,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you say so, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.58,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.78,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.29,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:09.46,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thank you for taking time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:12.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,from your busy schedules to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.06,B2,HITSUGAYA (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Never mind the formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.96,B2,HITSUGAYA (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,What’re we going to do from here on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:23.10,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve already sealed \Noff the Precipice World
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and rendered communications impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:29.57,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,We must unite before they can form
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a strategy and return here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:37.05,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,There are still a few captains who have
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,not been replaced with a Reigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.40,B2,NANAO (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,What’ll we do about the Head Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:45.40,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan in mind for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:49.45,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I will need \Neveryone’s help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.12,B2,KENPACHI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,I don’t care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.73,B2,KENPACHI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,I’ll listen to anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.50,B2,KENPACHI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,So how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:02.46,B2,KENPACHI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and let me fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:06.16,B2,MAYURI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how revolting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:09.43,B2,MAYURI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Barbarians are so eager to use violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.43,B2,KENPACHI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:14.86,B2,MAYURI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Not that I care whom a barbarian \Nchooses to fight, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:17.60,B2,MAYURI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Don’t go carving them up too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:21.81,B2,MAYURI (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,They’re my important test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.69,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,What are your thoughts, Captain Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:30.28,B2,BYAKUYA (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,There is only one head \Nof the Kuchiki Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.49,B2,BYAKUYA (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:35.30,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:42.61,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,All your wishes will soon be realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:46.78,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Once we have captured that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.30,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,With these hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:55.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we will transform the world \Ninto what it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.40,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,So much trouble for just one girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:10.93,OS,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reaper Imposter Crisis Committee Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.68,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we will now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,begin our Soul Reaper \Nimposter crisis meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:13.50,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,With your permission, \NI will be your host.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.66,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’s the matter, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.17,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even need to ask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:23.73,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why’re we in my room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.06,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:26.73,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Too many interruptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:35.11,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,The mastermind is Kageroza Inaba,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventh Seat in Squad 12
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and a section chief in the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:40.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Department of Research and Development.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:44.05,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,He controlled and studied \Nthe Precipice World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:46.98,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he’s a \NPrecipice World specialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.12,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,This Precipice World incident
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,was planned entirely by Kageroza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.07,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,He manipulated time \Nin the Precipice World
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:59.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so that we would be met by the Cleaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.83,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,He confined us there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.71,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,and sent back Reigai versions of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the captains to the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.40,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,If left unchecked,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the entire Thirteen Court Guard Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,will be under his control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.44,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,How aggravating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:22.73,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Kageroza…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.68,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,He lured me to the Soul Society by
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,manipulating the Thirteen \NCourt Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:31.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, he \Ntried to capture Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:36.74,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What is he planning to use Nozomi for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.70,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,In all likelihood,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:44.42,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,that girl holds some huge secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.20,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,For example,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he may have hidden something \Ninside that girl’s body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:58.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:03.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll never let something \Nlike that happen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:10.46,OS,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA’S SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.44,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Urahara…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.29,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:18.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,for providing us this barbeque \Nset and the food too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:21.54,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. Don’t mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.41,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s enjoy it together later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.52,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,A barbeque?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:36.48,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you’re even \Ndumber than Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.43,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:44.67,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,This is Inoue’s way of \Ntrying to cheer her up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:49.34,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,That girl’s been though a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:55.52,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,I understand Inoue’s intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but should we be doing something \Nlike this during a crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:03.04,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, this activity could \Nhelp her open up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.29,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:11.25,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everybody! Let’s get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.82,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, would you mind \Ncutting the vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.04,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Sado, you get the fire started, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:16.90,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.23,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.18,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:34.61,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What? Goofing off already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:42.46,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry… This is your welcome party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.83,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if no one else, I want \Nyou to tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.75,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll help you any way I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:54.75,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it’s something you don’t
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,want to tell the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you can tell me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.79,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I did save your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.26,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.38,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.15,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That thing you’re holding there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:15.15,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s just chili powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.87,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Why’re you holding chili powder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.40,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.50,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t know what \Nchili powder is, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:25.57,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’m right, aren’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:28.45,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then I’ll teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:32.67,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Chili powder is awfully \Nspicy if you eat it as-is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.59,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,and when you put it directly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.50,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,into the mouth like that, it’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.51,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.55,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,My mouth is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.40,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:50.64,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.32,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.36,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.49,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:06.45,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve defiled the proud Quincy Cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.41,B2,KON (M),0000,0000,0000,,But that’s a shiitake mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.58,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a specially prepared shiitake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.79,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it with the appreciation \Nit deserves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.92,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:23.81,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.89,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi’s gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:27.36,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.03,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.52,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.27,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.27,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:43.65,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:48.83,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck could Nozomi have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.32,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:55.54,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.25,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:58.65,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:02.21,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve been looking for you, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.18,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Nozomi. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.72,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Come back and let’s \Nhave some barbeque.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:16.81,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.83,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be like that. Let’s go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:23.30,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone’s preparing it just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:25.82,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,C’mon, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:27.78,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone’s worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:32.75,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.09,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.13,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,We’re trying to cheer you up because
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we thought you’d be scared \Nafter being targeted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.97,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,And you say that’s not your concern?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.60,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you respond \Nto people’s kindness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:03.90,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.36,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.13,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.50,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.96,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,W-What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.93,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me out, Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:32.42,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That chick is cocky, violent, goes off
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:35.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,on her own and doesn’t \Nlisten to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:37.89,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,We’re trying to look after her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but she doesn’t appreciate it one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.11,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Even I’ve had it with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.38,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:47.99,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what’s going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but you seem to be having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:59.34,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:14:59.83,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:03.02,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Girls her age are difficult, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.38,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle this woman-to-woman, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:06.92,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:08.53,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That’d be a great help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:13.04,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but everyone is looking for Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:15.96,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Which means if I go back without her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:18.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they’ll get on my case again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.80,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:23.61,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,I’ll convince her to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.57,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,But, I’m a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:30.70,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,A man must keep his promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.44,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:32.95,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.99,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle this. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.66,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,She’s all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.80,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s talk over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.38,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:57.83,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That’s such a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.79,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,If that chick were a little more open,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:02.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,she might even be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.73,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,But Rangiku, now she’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.26,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me handle this. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:11.24,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.24,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.91,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.08,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.74,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rangiku… Why’re you—?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.54,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.13,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.15,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven’t seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.50,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.94,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Kon, what’re you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:38.37,B2,KON (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:39.90,B2,KON (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It’s my fault. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.85,B2,KON (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I let her out of my sight. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.52,B2,RUKIA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It’s an important assignment. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.28,B2,RUKIA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’m counting on you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:58.41,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.37,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.26,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Now then…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.80,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Let’s talk on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.81,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Now you’ve done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.75,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.30,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it took so long, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:36.38,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I saw through your guise \Nfrom the very start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:41.95,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Don’t interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.27,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you imposter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.76,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:50.88,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.17,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Imposter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.95,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Who’re you calling an imposter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.68,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,From here on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.19,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,we’re the real ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.38,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:18.43,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi… Hurry and get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:23.37,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry, I’ll \Ndefeat that imposter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:26.02,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! You can’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:27.21,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:30.27,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I left you alone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.03,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.29,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:10.05,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think you \Ncould stop me with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.04,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,You sure underestimated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.97,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Now then… Shall we go, Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.81,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.76,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,But before that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:28.77,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,You need to be punished \Nfor being a bad girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:37.32,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.04,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,It ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.95,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, you imposter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.88,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,So this is my imposter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.09,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,She’s quite a fine woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:59.55,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,But no match for the original, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.79,B2,RANGIKU (REIGAI),0000,0000,0000,,Growl, Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.85,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,She got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:27.49,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:29.45,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’m glad you’re okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:33.33,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it’s all thanks \Nto my awesome feats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:40.22,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Show some appreciation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.63,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.49,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:48.47,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This all started because you \Ntook your eyes off of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave her by \Nherself in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.50,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t Rukia make \Nit very clear to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.90,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…I…umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:56.57,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Perverted freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:57.69,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,No, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:02.48,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, Nozomi… The meat is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:05.16,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I’ll bring it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.61,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.72,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:13.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, we’ll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.96,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you people stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:19.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:21.76,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.97,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Have some barbeque! It’s delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.08,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:21.97,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,This sure turned out to be quite a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:23.10,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Not entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.10,0:23:24.90,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Having two Marechiyo Omaedas would
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:26.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,equate to twice the consumption \Nof fried rice crackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:28.39,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Having two Rangiku Matsumoto would
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:30.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,equate to having two Soul \NReapers who won’t do work,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.24,0:23:31.55,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,while having two Kenpachi \NZaraki would equate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:33.55,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,to double the destruction \Nbeing done. That’s all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:34.89,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.88,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:40.30,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me out, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:44.11,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,My Reigai had a wrinkle right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:46.44,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe they would \Ngo through the trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:48.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,just to add something like \Nthat for a sick joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:49.70,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:52.41,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but \Nthe Reigai he developed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:55.91,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,are perfect copies of ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:24:00.06,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-Must replenish my \Ncollagen supply with…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.06,0:24:00.83,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:02.83,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Meat, meat, meat, meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:04.55,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,My meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.55,0:24:06.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,